<BaseLayout title="Contact Construction Cost Calculator" description="Contact the Construction Cost Calculator website team with feedback or correction requests." canonicalPath="/contact/"><div class="container content-page"><span class="section-kicker">Contact</span><h1>Questions or Feedback?</h1><p>Found a calculation issue, unclear instruction, or accessibility problem? We welcome concise feedback that helps make these planning tools more useful.</p><h2>Email</h2><p><a href={`mailto:${site.email}`}>{site.email}</a></p><p>Please do not send confidential project documents or request a professional construction quote. This website does not provide contractor, engineering, or architectural services.</p></div></BaseLayout>
